data.description: 10K IN PREPAIDS OR POINT BUY DOWNS IS BEING OFFERED BY SELLER: This 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom Bluffton home is bigger than you would expect. You have high ceilings on the first floor, oversized cabinets, large corner pantry, granite counters and tons of storage perfect for any buyer, the epitome of open concept. The 2nd floor has all 4 bedrooms which will surprise you immediately with the great natural light, size and closet space. The owners suite is massive and with double vanity and double closets in the owners bath. STOP and take look this backyard, more than 25K in fencing already complete, possibilities are endless. MAKE YOUR APPOINTMENT!
